description: When Jace Chambers recognizes club dancer Giovanni Rosa at his gym, he wonders what else they might have in common. Jace has a thing for strippers, which is perfect, because Giovanni has a thing for guys with really big dicks, and Jace certainly has the goods to deliver on that account. Luckily for the two of them, no one is around, so they help themselves to a little post workout quality time, as Giovanni gets to know his new favorite customer, and Jace gets to sample the goods first hand. Enjoy!
title: The Warm Up
